### 배송 등록 요청 (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/deliveries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceNumber": "ABC123456",
  "status": "PREPARING",
  "expectedArrivalDate": "2025-09-21T15:00:00"
}

###

### 배송 조회 요청 (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/deliveries/ABC123456

### 없는 송장번호 조회 (GET) - 404 확인
GET http://localhost:8080/deliveries/NO_SUCH_INVOICE
Accept: application/json

###

### 배송 상태 변경 (PUT) - 상태 변경 API 만들고 테스트 예시
PUT http://localhost:8080/deliveries/ABC123456/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "SHIPPED"
}

###

### 잘못된 데이터 보내기 (POST) - status 누락 및 잘못된 값
POST http://localhost:8080/deliveries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceNumber": "XYZ7891011",
  "status": "INVALID_STATUS",
  "expectedArrivalDate": "2025-09-25T12:00:00"
}

###

POST http://localhost:8080/deliveries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expectedArrivalDate": "2025-09-25T12:00:00"
}

###

### 전체 배송 목록 조회 (GET) - 목록 API 구현 후 테스트
GET http://localhost:8080/deliveries
Accept: application/json

###

### 도착 예정일 계산 테스트 (추후 구현)
POST http://localhost:8080/deliveries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceNumber": "CALC123456",
  "status": "PREPARING"
}

GET http://localhost:8080/deliveries/CALC123456
Accept: application/json

